aaa306f2-c8a9-4b78-b977-6f58ca156954.Text: Lord Captain! Upon transitioning to realspace we have found ourselves among a number of starships belonging to the enemies of humanity! The augurs report they are readying their weapons and assuming an attack formation! What are your orders?

0f864c45-bff8-4b65-8a78-32ab427559c3.Text: Call the crew to battle stations, we will face them with valor.

368d304b-41b7-4c20-8b5c-1d1d4d115ff2.Text: Attempt to disengage, we are not prepared for this fight.
